d | authorlink = Ed Nimmervoll | archivedate = 29 January 2003 | accessdate = 4 August 2015 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Nostalgia Bio\">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20030506214338/http://www.nostalgiacentral.com/music/lrb.htm | url = http://nostalgiacentral.com/music/artists-l-to-z/artists-l/little-river-band-lrb/ | title = Little River Band (LRB) | work = Nostalgia Central | publisher = | archivedate = 6 May 2003 | accessdate = 4 August 2015 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Kimball D\">{{cite web | archiveurl = http://pandora.nla.gov.au/pan/35967/20080307-0002/www.milesago.com/Artists/drummond.html | url = http://www.milesago.com/artists/drummond.htm |title = Drummond | last1 = Kimball | first1 = Duncan | publisher = Milesago: Australasian Music and Popular Culture 1964\u20131975. Ice Productions | year = 2002 | archivedate = 7 March 2008 | accessdate = 4 August 2015 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Go-Set Charts Sep 71\">{{cite web | url = http://www.poparchives.com.au/gosetcharts/1971/19710918.html | last1 = Nimmervoll | first1 = Ed | work = [[Go-Set]] | title = National Top 40 | publisher = Waverley Press | date = 18 September 1971 | accessdate = 4 August 2015 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924095956/http://www.poparchives.com.au/gosetcharts/1971/19710918.html | archive-date = 24 September 2015 | url-status = live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"O'Connor\">{{cite web | url = http://www.aylesburyfriars.co.uk/interviewslittleriverband.html | title = Friars Interviews: Graeham Goble Little River Band | last = O'Connor | first = Mike | work = Aylesbury Friars | year = 2011 | accessdate = 4 August 2015 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150923181042/http://www.aylesburyfriars.co.uk/interviewslittleriverband.html | archive-date = 23 September 2015 | url-status = live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Wheatley\">{{cite book | author1 = Wheatley, Glenn | authorlink1 = Glenn Wheatley | title = Paper paradise: confessions of a rock 'n' roll survivor | public