bsg.html | archive-date = 23 September 2015 | url-status = live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Sams\">{{cite news | last1 = Sams | first1 = Christine | title = ARIAs reunite Little River Band | url = http://www.smh.com.au/articles/2004/09/11/1094789737961.html | accessdate = 13 January 2015 | work = The Sydney Morning Herald | publisher = Fairfax Media | date = 12 September 2004 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081007085534/http://www.smh.com.au/articles/2004/09/11/1094789737961.html | archive-date = 7 October 2008 | url-status = live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Federal\">{{cite web | publisher = [[Federal Court of Australia]] | date = 12 July 2002 | url = http://www.austlii.edu.au/au/cases/cth/federal_ct/2002/875.rtf | title = ''We Two Pty Ltd v Shorrock (2002)'' | accessdate = 8 August 2015 | format = [[Rich Text Format]] }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Eliezer\">{{cite journal | url = http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/1408691/original-little-river-band-win-legal-case | title = Original Little River Band Win Legal Case | author = Eliezer, Christie | work = Billboard | date = 28 July 2005 | accessdate = 8 August 2015 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Goble Taken\">{{cite web | title = Someone's Taken Our History | author = Goble, Graeham | url = http://www.graehamgoble.com/clips-goble | publisher = Graeham Goble Official Website | accessdate = 9 December 2012 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120321191947/http://graehamgoble.com/clips-goble | archive-date = 21 March 2012 | url-status = live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Birtles Door\">{{cite web | last = Cashmere | first = Paul | authorlink = Paul Cashmere | title = Beeb Birtles Says Screw You to Current Little River Band | url = http://www.noise11.com/news/beeb-birtles-says-screw-you-to-current-little-river-band-20121209 | work = noise11.com | publisher = Paul Cashmere, Ros O'Gorman | accessdate = 9 December 2012 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130610014532/http://www.noise11.com/news/beeb-birtles-says-screw-you-to-current-little-river-band-20121209 | archive-date = 10 June 2013 | url-status = live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Wardlaw 1\">{{cite web | url = http://ultimateclassicrock.com/little-river-band-2015-interview/ | title = Little River Band\u2019s Wayne Nelson Talks About ''Tonight Show'' Appearance \u2013 Exclusive Interview | author = Wardlaw, Matt | publisher = Townsquare Media | work = Ultimate Classic Rock | date = 9 January 2015 | accessdate = 8 August 2015 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150717102723/http://ultimateclassicrock.com/little-river-band-2015-interview/ | archive-date = 17 July 2015 | url-status = live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Cornwall\">{{cite web | url = http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-01-10/tonight-shows-request-reignites-bitter-little-river-band-feud/6010254 | title = Jimmy Fallon's Tonight Show request reignites bitter Little River Band feud | last = Cornwall | first = Deborah | work = [[ABC News (Australia)|ABC News]] | publisher = Australian Broadcasting Corporation (ABC) | accessdate = 8 August 2015 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150820060154/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-01-10/tonight-shows-request-reignites-bitter-little-river-band-feud/6010254 | archive-date = 20 August 2015 | url-status = live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Cashmere 2\">{{cite web | last1 = Cashmere | first1 = Paul | title = Little River Band Show Cancelled Over Upfront Payment Dispute | url = http://www.noise11.com/news/little-river-band-show-cancelled-over-upfront-payment-dispute-20150328 | website = noise11.com | publisher = Paul Cashmere, Ros O'Gorman | accessdate = 28 May 2015 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150528063532/http://www.noise11.com/news/little-river-band-show-cancelled-over-upfront-payment-dispute-20150328 | archive-date = 28 May 2015 | url-status = live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Music VF\">{{cite web|title=Little River Band Top Songs|url=http://www.musicvf.com/Little+River+Band.art|website=musicvf.com|accessdat