ive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150119033310/http://web.ncf.ca/fl512/beatles/interviews/2003-09-23.htm|archive-date=19 January 2015|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Prestwich Obit\">{{ cite news | url = http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/arts/last-wave-of-summer-for-cold-chisel-drummer-steve-prestwich/story-e6frg8n6-1225989829247 | title = Last wave of summer for Cold Chisel drummer Steve Prestwich | work = [[The Australian]] | publisher = [[News Corp Australia]] | date = 18 January 2011 | accessdate = 8 August 2015 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Sullivan Obit\">{{cite web | archiveurl = http://pandora.nla.gov.au/pan/35967/20090315-0738/www.milesago.com/Obits/big-goose-obit.html | url = http://www.milesago.com/Obits/big-goose-obit.htm | title = Obituaries \u2013 Barry 'Big Goose' Sullivan | last1 = Kimball | first1 = Duncan | publisher = Milesago: Australasian Music and Popular Culture 1964\u20131975. Ice Productions | year = 2002 | archivedate = 15 March 2009 | accessdate = 8 August 2015 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"APRA Awards\">\nLittle River Band at the [[APRA Awards (Australia)|APRA Music Awards]]:\n* 1982:&nbsp;{{cite web | url = http://apraamcos.com.au/awards/1980-1989/1982-music-awards/ | title = 1982 Music Awards | publisher = Australasian Performing Right Association | accessdate = 9 August 2015 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150927111602/http://apraamcos.com.au/awards/1980-1989/1982-music-awards/ | archive-date = 27 September 2015 | url-status = live }}\n* 1984:&nbsp;{{cite web | url = http://apraamcos.com.au/awards/1980-1989/1984-music-awards/ | title = 1984 Music Awards | publisher = Australasian Performing Right Association | accessdate = 9 August 2015 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150927111522/http://apraamcos.com.au/awards/1980-1989/1984-music-awards/ | archive-date = 27 September 2015 | url-status = live }}\n* 1985:&nbsp;{{cite web | url = http://apraamcos.com.au/awards/1980-1989/1985-music-awards/ | title = 1985 Music Awards | publisher = Australasian Performing Right Association | accessdate = 9 August 2015 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150927111516/http://apraamcos.com.au/awards/1980-1989/1985-music-awards/ | archive-date = 27 September 2015 | url-status = live }}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ARMA 77\">Australian Rock Music Awards of 1977:\n* Nominations:&nbsp;{{cite news | url = http://nla.gov.au/nla.news-article110881776 | title = Rock music awards on 2CC | newspaper = The Canberra Times | date = 8 December 1977 | accessdate = 9 August 2015 | page = 22 | publisher = National Library of Australia}}\n* Winners:&nbsp;{{cite news | url = http://nla.gov.au/nla.news-article110882349 | title = Timespan Australian rock-music awards | newspaper = The Canberra Times | date = 10 December 1977 | accessdate = 9 August 2015 | page = 11 | publisher = National Library of Australia}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"DPAA\">{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ELACebeQEgcC |title=The dictionary of performing arts in Australia |last=Atkinson |first=Ann |author2=Linsay Knight |author3=Margaret McPhee  |publisher=[[Allen & Unwin]] |year=1996 |isbn=978-1-86373-898-9 | accessdate = 5 December 2008 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Top40TV\">{{cite web | url = http://users.ncable.net.au/~ronjeff/top40/oz_king.htm | title = Australian Music Awards | publisher = Ron Jeff | accessdate = 16 December 2010 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110706123804/http://users.ncable.net.au/~ronjeff/top40/oz_king.htm | archive-date = 6 July 2011 | url-status = live }}</ref>\n}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Official website|www.littleriverband.com/}}\n* [http://colsearch.nfsa.gov.au/nfsa/search/summary/summary.w3p;adv=no;group=;groupequals=;page=0;parentid=;query=Organisation%3A%22%2FOrganisation%2Fkey%2F20606-1%22;querytype=;resCount=10 Little River Band holdings in the National Film and Sound Archive]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20170427153333/http://www.yuzu-melodies.fr/Little-River-Band-L-A-was-